com.beardedhen.androidbootstrap.api.attributes

Interface BootstrapBrand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultBootstrapBrand

    public interface BootstrapBrand
extends java.io.Serializable
    A Bootstrap Brand is a color which is used universally across many Bootstrap Views. An example is the 'Info' Brand which colors views light blue.
